          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Hammers' Law</b></p> <p>This bill makes additional compensation recoverable for nonpecuniary damages (but not punitive damages) for deaths resulting from a passenger cruise ship accident occurring on the high seas beyond 12 nautical miles from the U.S. shore.</p>]]></text>
